      • saveToFile

        public int saveToFile(Molecule molsToSave,
                      URL urlFileName,
                      SelectExpression expr)
        Saves molecules into a file. If selection expression is provided, then it is used to determine which molecules/chains/residues/atoms to save. If not, then selected atoms are saved.
        Parameters:
        molsToSave - list of molecules to be saved.
        urlFileName - name of file on the web to save.
        expr - selection expression for atoms.
        Returns:
        number of atoms saved. Negative if error happend.
